#. module: account_peppol
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/account_peppol/exceptions.py:0
msgid ""
"A Receipt has been received  for a message that was previously sent by the "
"MSH generating this error, but the content does not match the message "
"content (e.g. some part has not been acknowledged, or the digest associated "
"does not match the signature digest, for NRR)."
msgstr ""
"ໄດ້ຮັບໃບຢັ້ງຢືນການຮັບສຳລັບຂໍ້ຄວາມທີ່ເຄີຍສົ່ງໂດຍ MSH ທີ່ສ້າງຂໍ້ຜິດພາດນີ້, ແຕ່ເນື້ອໃນບໍ່ກົງກັບເນື້ອໃນຂໍ້ຄວາມ "
"(ຕົວຢ່າງ: ບາງສ່ວນບໍ່ໄດ້ຮັບການຢືນຢືນ, ຫຼື digest ທີ່ກ່ຽວຂ້ອງບໍ່ກົງກັບ signature digest ສຳລັບ NRR)."

#. module: account_peppol
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/account_peppol/exceptions.py:0
msgid ""
"A Receipt has not been received  for a message that was previously sent by "
"the MSH generating this error."
msgstr "ຍັງບໍ່ທັນໄດ້ຮັບໃບຢັ້ງຢືນການຮັບສຳລັບຂໍ້ຄວາມທີ່ເຄີຍສົ່ງໂດຍ MSH ທີ່ສ້າງຂໍ້ຜິດພາດນີ້."

#. module: account_peppol
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/account_peppol/wizard/peppol_registration.py:0
msgid "A connection to '%s' already exists."
msgstr ""

#. module: account_peppol
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/account_peppol/exceptions.py:0
msgid ""
"A fragment is received but a previously received fragment message had the "
"same values for GroupId and FragmentNum"
msgstr ""
"ໄດ້ຮັບສ່ວນຍ່ອຍ (fragment) ແຕ່ຂໍ້ຄວາມສ່ວນຍ່ອຍທີ່ໄດ້ຮັບມາກ່ອນໜ້ານີ້ມີຄ່າ GroupId ແລະ FragmentNum "
"ຄືກັນ"

#. module: account_peppol
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/account_peppol/exceptions.py:0
msgid ""
"A fragment is received but more than one fragment message in a group of "
"fragments specifies a value for a compression element."
msgstr ""
"ໄດ້ຮັບສ່ວນຍ່ອຍ ແຕ່ມີຂໍ້ຄວາມສ່ວນຍ່ອຍຫຼາຍກວ່າໜຶ່ງຂໍ້ຄວາມໃນກຸ່ມສ່ວນຍ່ອຍທີ່ລະບຸຄ່າສຳລັບອົງປະກອບການບີບອັດ."

#. module: account_peppol
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/account_peppol/exceptions.py:0
msgid ""
"A fragment is received but more than one fragment message in a group of "
"fragments specifies a value for this element."
msgstr "ໄດ້ຮັບສ່ວນຍ່ອຍ ແຕ່ມີຂໍ້ຄວາມສ່ວນຍ່ອຍຫຼາຍກວ່າໜຶ່ງຂໍ້ຄວາມໃນກຸ່ມສ່ວນຍ່ອຍທີ່ລະບຸຄ່າສຳລັບອົງປະກອບນີ້."

#. module: account_peppol
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/account_peppol/exceptions.py:0
msgid ""
"A fragment is received that relates to a group that was previously rejected."
msgstr "ໄດ້ຮັບສ່ວນຍ່ອຍທີ່ກ່ຽວຂ້ອງກັບກຸ່ມທີ່ເຄີຍຖືກປະຕິເສດມາກ່ອນ."

#. module: account_peppol
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/account_peppol/exceptions.py:0
msgid ""
"A message unit in a bundle was not processed because a related message unit "
"in the bundle caused an error."
msgstr ""
"ໜ່ວຍຂໍ້ຄວາມໃນຊຸດ (bundle) ບໍ່ໄດ້ຮັບການປະມວນຜົນ "
"ເນື່ອງຈາກໜ່ວຍຂໍ້ຄວາມທີ່ກ່ຽວຂ້ອງໃນຊຸດນັ້ນເຮັດໃຫ້ເກີດຂໍ້ຜິດພາດ."

#. module: account_peppol
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/account_peppol/models/res_company.py:0
msgid ""
"A participant with these details has already been registered on the network. "
"If you have previously registered to a Peppol service, please deregister."
msgstr ""
"ຜູ້ເຂົ້າຮ່ວມທີ່ມີລາຍລະອຽດເຫຼົ່ານີ້ໄດ້ຖືກລົງທະບຽນໃນເຄືອຂ່າຍແລ້ວ. ຖ້າທ່ານເຄີຍລົງທະບຽນກັບບໍລິການ Peppol "
"ມາກ່ອນ, ກະລຸນາຍົກເລີກການລົງທະບຽນ."

#. module: account_peppol
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/account_peppol/models/res_company.py:0
msgid "A purchase journal must be used to receive Peppol documents."
msgstr "ຕ້ອງໃຊ້ປຶ້ມບັນຊີການຊື້ເພື່ອຮັບເອກະສານ Peppol."

#. module: account_peppol
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/account_peppol/exceptions.py:0
msgid ""
"A responding MSH indicates that it applies the alternate MEP binding to the "
"response message."
msgstr "MSH ທີ່ຕອບສະໜອງລະບຸວ່າມັນນຳໃຊ້ MEP binding ທາງເລືອກກັບຂໍ້ຄວາມຕອບກັບ."

#. module: account_peppol
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/account_peppol/exceptions.py:0
msgid ""
"A value is set for FragmentCount, but a previously received fragment had a "
"greature value."
msgstr "ມີການຕັ້ງຄ່າສຳລັບ FragmentCount, ແຕ່ສ່ວນຍ່ອຍທີ່ໄດ້ຮັບມາກ່ອນໜ້ານີ້ມີຄ່າທີ່ໃຫຍ່ກວ່າ."

#. module: account_peppol
#: model:ir.model,name:account_peppol.model_account_edi_proxy_client_user
msgid "Account EDI proxy user"
msgstr "ຜູ້ໃຊ້ຕົວແທນ EDI ຂອງບັນຊີ"

#. module: account_peppol
