#. module: account_peppol
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/account_peppol/exceptions.py:0
msgid ""
"Although the message document is well formed and schema valid, some element/"
"attribute contains a value that could not be recognized and therefore could "
"not be used by the MSH."
msgstr ""
"ເຖິງແມ່ນວ່າເອກະສານຂໍ້ຄວາມຈະຖືກຕ້ອງຕາມຮູບແບບ ແລະ schema, ແຕ່ບາງອົງປະກອບ/"
"ຄຸນລັກສະນະມີຄ່າທີ່ບໍ່ສາມາດຮັບຮູ້ໄດ້ ແລະ ດັ່ງນັ້ນ MSH ຈຶ່ງບໍ່ສາມາດນຳໃຊ້ໄດ້."

#. module: account_peppol
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/account_peppol/exceptions.py:0
msgid ""
"Although the message document is well formed and schema valid, some element/"
"attribute value cannot be processed as expected because the related feature "
"is not supported by the MSH."
msgstr ""
"ເຖິງແມ່ນວ່າເອກະສານຂໍ້ຄວາມຈະຖືກຕ້ອງຕາມຮູບແບບ ແລະ schema, ແຕ່ຄ່າບາງອົງປະກອບ/"
"ຄຸນລັກສະນະບໍ່ສາມາດປະມວນຜົນໄດ້ຕາມທີ່ຄາດໄວ້ ເນື່ອງຈາກຄຸນສົມບັດທີ່ກ່ຽວຂ້ອງບໍ່ໄດ້ຮັບການສະໜັບສະໜູນໂດຍ MSH."

#. module: account_peppol
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/account_peppol/exceptions.py:0
msgid ""
"Although the message document is well formed and schema valid, some element/"
"attribute value is inconsistent either with the content of other element/"
"attribute, or with the processing mode of the MSH, or with the normative "
"requirements of the ebMS specification."
msgstr ""
"ເຖິງແມ່ນວ່າເອກະສານຂໍ້ຄວາມຈະຖືກຕ້ອງຕາມຮູບແບບ ແລະ schema, ແຕ່ຄ່າບາງອົງປະກອບ/"
"ຄຸນລັກສະນະບໍ່ສອດຄ່ອງກັບເນື້ອໃນຂອງອົງປະກອບ/ຄຸນລັກສະນະອື່ນໆ, ຫຼືກັບຮູບແບບການປະມວນຜົນຂອງ MSH, "
"ຫຼືກັບຂໍ້ກຳນົດມາດຕະຖານຂອງຂໍ້ກຳນົດ ebMS."

#. module: account_peppol
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/account_peppol/exceptions.py:0
msgid ""
"Although the message document is well formed and schema valid, the presence "
"or absence of some element/ attribute is not consistent with the capability "
"of the MSH, with respect to supported features."
msgstr ""
"ເຖິງແມ່ນວ່າເອກະສານຂໍ້ຄວາມຈະຖືກຕ້ອງຕາມຮູບແບບ ແລະ schema, ແຕ່ການມີ ຫຼື ບໍ່ມີຂອງບາງອົງປະກອບ/"
"ຄຸນລັກສະນະບໍ່ສອດຄ່ອງກັບຄວາມສາມາດຂອງ MSH ໃນດ້ານຄຸນສົມບັດທີ່ຮອງຮັບ."

#. module: account_peppol
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/account_peppol/exceptions.py:0
msgid ""
"Although the message was sent under Guaranteed delivery requirement, the "
"Reliability module could not get assurance that the message was properly "
"delivered, in spite of resending efforts."
msgstr ""
"ເຖິງແມ່ນວ່າຂໍ້ຄວາມຈະຖືກສົ່ງພາຍໃຕ້ຂໍ້ກຳນົດການສົ່ງທີ່ຮັບປະກັນ, "
"ແຕ່ໂມດູນຄວາມໜ້າເຊື່ອຖືບໍ່ສາມາດໝັ້ນໃຈໄດ້ວ່າຂໍ້ຄວາມຖືກສົ່ງຢ່າງຖືກຕ້ອງ, "
"ເຖິງແມ່ນວ່າຈະມີຄວາມພະຍາຍາມສົ່ງໃໝ່ກໍຕາມ."

#. module: account_peppol
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/account_peppol/exceptions.py:0
msgid ""
"An Intermediary MSH was unable to route an ebMS message and stopped "
"processing the message."
msgstr "MSH ຕົວກາງບໍ່ສາມາດກຳນົດເສັ້ນທາງຂໍ້ຄວາມ ebMS ແລະ ຢຸດການປະມວນຜົນຂໍ້ຄວາມນັ້ນ."

#. module: account_peppol
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/account_peppol/exceptions.py:0
msgid ""
"An MSH has determined that the message is expired and will not attempt to "
"forward or deliver it."
msgstr "MSH ໄດ້ກຳນົດວ່າຂໍ້ຄວາມໝົດອາຍຸແລ້ວ ແລະ ຈະບໍ່ພະຍາຍາມສົ່ງຕໍ່ ຫຼື ສົ່ງມອບມັນ."

#. module: account_peppol
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/account_peppol/exceptions.py:0
msgid ""
"An entry in the routing function is matched that assigns the message to an "
"MPC for pulling, but the intermediary MSH is unable to store the message "
"with this MPC"
msgstr ""
"ລາຍການໃນຟັງຊັນການກຳນົດເສັ້ນທາງກົງກັນເຊິ່ງມອບໝາຍຂໍ້ຄວາມໃຫ້ MPC ສຳລັບການດຶງຂໍ້ມູນ, ແຕ່ MSH "
"ຕົວກາງບໍ່ສາມາດຈັດເກັບຂໍ້ຄວາມດ້ວຍ MPC ນີ້ໄດ້"

#. module: account_peppol
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/account_peppol/exceptions.py:0
msgid "An error occurred during the decompression."
msgstr "ເກີດຂໍ້ຜິດພາດໃນລະຫວ່າງການບີບຂໍ້ມູນອອກ (decompression)."

#. module: account_peppol
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/account_peppol/exceptions.py:0
msgid "An error occurred while decompressing the reassembled message."
msgstr "ເກີດຂໍ້ຜິດພາດໃນຂະນະທີ່ບີບຂໍ້ມູນອອກຂອງຂໍ້ຄວາມທີ່ປະກອບໃໝ່."

#. module: account_peppol
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/account_peppol/exceptions.py:0
msgid ""
"An incoming message fragment has a a value greater than the known "
"FragmentCount."
msgstr "ສ່ວນຍ່ອຍຂອງຂໍ້ຄວາມທີ່ເຂົ້າມາມີຄ່າຫຼາຍກວ່າ FragmentCount ທີ່ຮູ້ຈັກ."

#. module: account_peppol
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/account_peppol/exceptions.py:0
msgid ""
"An intermediary MSH has assigned the message to an MPC for pulling and has "
"successfully stored it. However the intermediary set a limit on the time it "
"was prepared to wait for the message to be pulled, and that limit has been "
"reached."
msgstr ""
"MSH ຕົວກາງໄດ້ມອບໝາຍຂໍ້ຄວາມໃຫ້ MPC ສຳລັບການດຶງຂໍ້ມູນ ແລະ ຈັດເກັບມັນສຳເລັດແລ້ວ. ຢ່າງໃດກໍຕາມ, "
"ຕົວກາງໄດ້ກຳນົດເວລາລໍຖ້າການດຶງຂໍ້ຄວາມ ແລະ ເວລານັ້ນໄດ້ໝົດລົງແລ້ວ."

#. module: account_peppol
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/account_peppol/exceptions.py:0
msgid "An internal error occurred"
msgstr "ເກີດຂໍ້ຜິດພາດພາຍໃນ"

